{"tid":967914,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"見到當日d企街基層地產仔漸漸變中年呀叔，一事無成","createTime":"2019-01-03T23:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T06:27:49.000Z","uid":40470,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4bbf77eecb15633df464ef9d6d5c2eedfb9e23","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心都涼晒<br />\n<br />\n呢班柒頭，低學歷，無技能<br />\n<br />\n靠地產霸拳搶客呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能總有短暫風光日子過過<br />\n<br />\n但對社會毫無供獻<br />\n<br />\n搭經濟順風車搵到過少少錢就自以為是<br />\n<br />\n你睇今日<br />\n<br />\n你人到中年仲戇鳩鳩要起街乞人買樓<br />\n<br />\n收入卻越來越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抵撚死，真係抵撚你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上半世呃呃氹氹一事無成<br />\n<br />\n下半世有排你挨呀死乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c561aa248cdb178589111afb4bc7a8daefb52e","tid":967914,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:28:22.000Z","msg":"眼紅？"},{"pid":"3eb513f42acfb762a2f468d548c7d91ba16c0c78","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:28:34.000Z","msg":"善惡到頭終有報<br />\n<br />\n多行不義必自斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0b31d96a3130dfa50de056cc722e5125754d7f","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"61c561aa248cdb178589111afb4bc7a8daefb52e","tid":967914,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:28:22.000Z","msg":"眼紅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:28:55.000Z","msg":"AA9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3988e12e1f446763c26996b2f1361831e0656583","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:29:05.000Z","msg":"青山道見到呢個post會唔會好憤怒？<br />\n<br />\n係呀講緊你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eb1b77c78e8afd4963685f08b89e61ec88c7dd","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:49:26.000Z","msg":"呢班基層地產佬日日有乜做？<br />\n<br />\n坐地產舖無所事事又一日<br />\n<br />\n成日煩鳩住人打比你<br />\n<br />\nBlock左一個電話<br />\n<br />\n佢就133打來<br />\n<br />\nBlock埋133<br />\n<br />\n佢就換個電話打來繼續叫你放盤比佢做<br />\n<br />\n社會廢物"},{"pid":"22e6956958b322c86f587a2aa14d2851c569c9b5","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"呢班傻鳩<br />\n<br />\n佢老細叫佢企街乞人買樓佢唔用腦就照做<br />\n<br />\n其實又會有幾多人<br />\n<br />\n會經一個企街三尖八角唔識既柒頭買樓？"},{"pid":"6e8608d8a431bcbbf37828fb66df266c38203dfb","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"三五成群企街企商場叫人買樓<br />\n<br />\n少部份地產佬真心叫人買樓<br />\n<br />\n但其實成功機會微乎其微<br />\n<br />\n弱智你期望中六合彩就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他根本浪費時間<br />\n<br />\nMk地產企埋一堆嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n<br />\n企夠時間就安心夠資格拎佢地既底薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f4f7536a52bfdeff0e675111bd48ff539b29c6","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T23:59:53.000Z","msg":"你前半生做過d乜<br />\n<br />\n下半生會以倍數來承受其後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c09d32ba1f1f85c0301d49200147880ebf0a40","tid":967914,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bebed65b2e048b2f5555ceaac7145d0c34909ad","tid":967914,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"痴左咩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353c4253213ff995827edb47509ce5e449de27ef","tid":967914,"uid":89869,"l